title: The Time Tunnel - Invasion Ep. 15
description: Doug and Tony are transported to the Cherbourg Penisula on 04 June 1944, forty-eight hours before the D-Day. Doug and Tony are captured by the Gestapo after an attack of the French underground resistance. Doug is submitted as subject to an experiment of Dr. Hans Kleinemann and he is brainwashed and reprogrammed to kill Tony. Meanwhile Dr. Kleinemann asks Major Hoffman to let Tony escape as part of his experiment. However, Tony is captured by three members of the resistance and has to prove that he is not German.
